menu_content_crimefest_desc = "",--In October the OVERKILL crew celebrated that PAYDAY turned 3 years old by throwing Crimefest, a 12 day long celebration between October 16-27. There were no less than 7 in-game updates made - all for free - as well as news about upcoming content. We also hosted the 2 hour Crimefest live stream with the Creatures in the Monster Energy DreamHack Studio in Stockholm. Old Hoxton, John Wick and the Hoxton Breakout heist were all released during the event. Last but not least, we finally opened the doors to our merchandise store at store.overkillsoftware.com.
